  <brief_title>Safety and Blood Donations in Adults Vaccinated With rMenB+OMV NZ.</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase 3b, Open Label, Uncontrolled, Single-arm, Single-centre Study to Evaluate the Safety of Two Doses of Novartis Meningococcal Group B Vaccine When Administered to Healthy Adults From 18 to 50 Years of Age and to Collect Blood Donations to Develop Vaccines Against Neisseria Meningitidis</official_title>
