  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this trial is to assess the safety of a Meningococcal Group B Vaccine and to
      collect blood donation. Sera panel obtained from blood donations will be used as a control to
      measure the immunoresponse to the Meningococcal Group B Vaccine in other studies.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
